1.title: Vacances
1.plot: Laia and Ji Lan have great ideas for their holidays, but Olivia is planning something different.

2.title: Les tardes amb l'Olívia
2.plot: Olivia hosts her own talk show.

3.title: Conte de Nadal
3.plot: The three spirits of Christmas visit Olivia in an attempt to mend her ways.

4.title: Tontontorona
4.plot: Olivia just found out why boys are stupid.

5.title: Nois dolents
5.plot: Laia is having some problems with a boy and Olivia offers to help her.

6.title: Fama
6.plot: The girls discuss about their respective dream jobs.

7.title: Pau interior
7.plot: Nothing can disturb Ji Lan's inner peace, but Olivia and Laia are trying hard anyway.

8.title: El bronzejat
8.plot:

9.title: Matemàtiques
9.plot: Olivia gets an unexpected interest in mathematics.

10.title: Festa de pijames
10.plot: Laia and Ji Lan are forced to listen to Olivia's complaints after she finds out she isn't allowed to attend a party.

11.title: L'habitació s'encongeix
11.plot: The Virtual Room broke down and the girls are in danger.

12.title: Els diners de l'Olívia
12.plot: Olivia imagines the things she could do with 500 euros.

13.title: La llegenda de Sant Jordi
13.plot: The girls do their peculiar re-enactment of the legend of St. George.

14.title: Màgia
14.plot: Ji Lan does a spectacular magic trick, but Olivia is determined to top it.

15.title: El noi nou
15.plot: Olivia and Ji Lan have slightly different opinions about the new boy in school.

16.title: Wakama Natuchu
16.plot: Olivia sends a message to all the middle sisters of the world.

17.title: Cara d'àngel
17.plot: Betrayal, theft, mild off-screen violence, amateur detective work, and pretty fashion complements meet in the tragic noir story of Olivia and her landlord.

18.title: El concurs de guitarres d'aire
18.plot: Who'll win the first Virtual Room contest of playing guitar without a guitar?

19.title: Somnis
19.plot: Olivia had a dream last night, and her sisters try to guess what it was about.

20.title: Veu interior
20.plot: A mysterious voice is talking to Ji Lan!

21.title: Repetició
21.plot: Laia tries to have fun at Ji Lan's expense by repeating every single word she says.

22.title: Qui sóc?
22.plot: Ji Lan is sad because she thinks she failed an exam, and Olivia isn't doing much to cheer her up.

23.title: Una de pirates
23.plot: Laia is the most feared pirate in the Mediterranean Sea, but Olivia isn't an easy lady in distress to have around.

24.title: Festa sorpresa
24.plot: Olivia is convinced that her sisters are planning a surprise birthday party for her.

25.title: L'especial de Halloween
25.plot: Revolting horrors await Olivia inside the Virtual Room.

26.title: Torn de neteja
26.plot: It's Ji Lan's turn to clean the house... but she doesn't really feel like it.

27.title: Em fa mal la cara!
27.plot: Olivia claims she's so beautiful that her face actually hurts.

28.title: Imitació
28.plot: Olivia, Laia and Ji Lan play an imitation game.

29.title: Personatges històrics
29.plot: Laia, Olivia and Ji Lan fantasize about meeting their favorite historical figures.

30.title: Classes de vol
30.plot: Ji Lan tries to teach Laia her levitating technique.

31.title: Alegrant la Laia
31.plot: Ji Lan and Olivia compete to cheer Laia up.

32.title: El pols xinès
32.plot: Laia and Ji Lan engage in a deadly battle of thumbs.

33.title: Sentiments
33.plot: Olivia discovers she has sensitive side, but she's not sure she wants to have one.

34.title: La bufetada més fluixa
34.plot: Olivia wants to play a new game she has learned, but things get a little dangerous.

35.title: Poders
35.plot: Laia, Olivia and Ji Lan try to decide what's the best possible superpower.

36.title: Consells
36.plot: Ji Lan opens a brand new counseling service.

37.title: El joc
37.plot: When Laia logs in the Virtual Room, she finds Ji Lan and Olivia are standing still as a statue.

38.title: Cita amb en Timmy Wong
38.plot: What's the real story behind Laia and Timmy Wong's afternoon at the movies?

39.title: El retrat de l'Olívia
39.plot: Olivia's favorite work of art hides unimaginable surprises.

40.title: A la Ji Lan ja no li agrada el Tai Choy
40.plot: Ji Lan's unexpected decision to stop doing Tai Choy makes her sisters go crazy.

41.title: Carnestoltes
41.plot: Something about Laia's carnival costume is troubling her sisters.

42.title: La marginada
42.plot: Olivia can't decide what to do with her class' outcast girl.

43.title: Victòria
43.plot: Laia and Ji Lan face each other in an epic duel.

44.title: La màquina del temps
44.plot: Laia and Ji Lan try to escape Olivia by traveling through time.

45.title: El rap d'en Timmy Wong
45.plot: Laia's written a very special rap song and wants her sisters to hear it.

46.title: El gest de la Ji Lan
46.plot: Ji Lan's body language is spinning out of control.

47.title: Superlaia
47.plot: Laia is a comic book superhero.

48.title: Caramels
48.plot: Laia's eaten too much candy, and it wasn't even HER candy.

49.title: Consciència
49.plot: The girls face a moral dilemma that puts their conscience to test.

50.title: Literatura
50.plot: Olivia tries to mock poor Laia's ambition to become a writer.

51.title: Personalitat
51.plot: Laia, Olivia and Ji Lan decide it's time to turn their lives around.

52.title: El narrador deixa de narrar
52.plot: The Narrator decides to quit and go on vacation.

imdb.plot outline: It's 2374. Laia, Olivia and Ji Lan are three sisters who log in the Virtual Room, a private 3D chat where they can talk and live all kind of adventures. Laia is sporty and aggressive, although she's rather clumsy and not very good with boys. Olívia is apparently shallow but she's much more astute than she seems. She always uses her brains for evil purposes, though, Laia being her most usual victim. Ji Lan is smart and calm and spends quite a good amount of time trying to stop her sisters from fighting.
